name: Pois 17
description:
Enter in the volume of the open cup/vase. Pois 17 have been generated during an 100 days project/exploration in may 2016. 

Each “Pois” is an exploration between algorithmic and organic gesture. Each short motion is unique to the gesture that originated it. Created by Jean-Charles Amey using Processing, discover other “Pois” in the collection #100daysofpois.
